== Scientific work and research ==
His research activities focus on the fields Asian/Oriental studies:<ref>Critical view of his scientific work and research see: K. Kaucha, Kościelniak Krzysztof, in: Leksykon teologii fundamentalnej [Dictionary of Fundamental Theology] ed. M. Rusecki, Lublin-Kraków 2002, pp. 653-654; J. Hauziński, [Research on the history of the Islamic world in Poland after 1945] Badania nad dziejami świata islamu w Polsce po 1945 roku, in: T. Majda (ed.), Szkice z dziejów polskiej orientalistyki, vol. V, Warszawa 2010, pp. 69-70;</ref>

